text:
I woke up unusually early.
Must be because of work...

Good morning, Amana.
You're up early.

Yeah, I'm full of energy this morning~
Since I'm up, maybe I'll go for a walk.

Oh, that sounds nice.
Mind if I join you?

I'm not too familiar with this area yet,
so I might just wander aimlessly...

Hehe, yeah, it does!
Then, let's go exploring together~!
